- Plan Tier-1: codex BLOCK (verified-true, two concurrency defects Opus+gemini missed: context.WithTimeout doesn't bound a surviving-child pipe hang → cmd.WaitDelay; fi.Size() cap is a TOCTOU → io.LimitReader) → design amended; Opus+gemini GO.
- Implement Tier-1: UNANIMOUS GO (codex, gemini, Opus). Opus reproduced the no-hang both ways + verified cap off-by-one/fd-close + -race. Verify additionally found + fixed a test-speed regression (const→var WaitDelay) before the gate.
